---
// Gray call-out box used on /whatwedo and /who-we-are
---

<section class="callout">
  <div class="container callout-inner">
    <h2>Looking to further your career without losing your soul? We can help!</h2>
    <p>
      With over twenty years of Entertainment business experience and first-hand
      experience on the road, we know what it takes to grow a business around a
      creative vision. Don't wait – start today with a simple conversation.
    </p>
    <a href="/book-a-consultation/" class="btn">Schedule Free Conversation</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .callout {
    background: var(--color-gray-section);
    padding: 64px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .callout-inner { max-width: 760px; }

  .callout h2 { font-size: 26px; }

  .callout p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
</style>
